{-# OPTIONS --without-K --safe --no-sized-types --no-guardedness #-}

module Agda.Builtin.Equality where

infix 4 _≡_
data _≡_ {a} {A : Set a} (x : A) : A → Set a where
  instance refl : x ≡ x

{-# BUILTIN EQUALITY _≡_ #-}
